---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About Potent Quotes</h1>
    <div class="prose max-w-2xl">
      <p>Welcome to Potent Quotes, your source for inspiring and thought-provoking quotes. Our mission is to bring you meaningful content that can enrich your life and spark new perspectives.</p>
      
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>We believe that words have the power to inspire, motivate, and transform. Through our carefully curated collection of quotes, we aim to provide you with daily inspiration and wisdom.</p>
      
      <h2>How We Work</h2>
      <p>Our quotes are sourced from a variety of authors, thinkers, and leaders throughout history. Each quote is selected for its potential to resonate with readers and provoke meaningful reflection.</p>
      
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Have feedback or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you! Reach out to us through our contact page.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
